Class Weight

  • java.lang.Object
    • Weight
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable

    public class Weight
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable
    Class that represents the user's weight and body composition information on a given date. A user can record this information once a day and can change or delete it.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Marcelo Portella
    See Also:
    Serialized Form

      • setWeightDate

        public void setWeightDate(java.lang.String weightDate)

        Parameters:
